results.name: Number of codes having highest minimal Euclidean norm of any Type 4^Z self-dual code of length n over Z/4Z.
comment: There are two versions of this sequence, this and A111263. I am not sure which is correct.

G. Nebe, E. M. Rains and N. J. A. Sloane, Self-Dual Codes and Invariant Theory, Springer, Berlin, 2006.
E. M. Rains and N. J. A. Sloane, Self-dual codes, pp. 177-294 of Handbook of Coding Theory, Elsevier, 1998; (Abstract, pdf, ps).
